{"tid":2315683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不安] 屌那媽有冇人聽過蠟燭灣candle cove","createTime":"2020-12-07T10:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T04:52:19.000Z","uid":82917,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b586103a3c0464f70a96f2a200f6a93db64910e4","tid":2315683,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">貼鬼相死全家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/5lpg6y3.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2F5lpg6y3.amp&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=c9e09c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/5lpg6y3.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n在都市傳說中，有一個名叫蠟燭灣的故事就有着這樣的神秘感。相傳蠟燭灣是一部兒童片，它有着非常古怪的畫面和劇情，而最讓人毛骨悚然的是有很多人都對這一部木偶劇有印象，但是卻找不到任何和它有關的資料。<br />\n<br />\n蠟燭灣的故事最早出現在2009年一個名叫&quot;Creepy Pasta&quot;的著名的恐怖故事網上，故事的大意是一個網友在一個名叫&quot;Net Nostalgia&quot; 的討論區中提問有沒有人記得蠟燭灣這個兒童節目。發帖人說這個節目是1971-1972在俄亥俄州當地電視台播放的，內容則是講述了一個名為&quot;Percy&quot;的海盜的故事。但海盜的身體由其他木偶的殘肢組成，外觀非常詭異。<br />\n<br />\n而緊接着的便是越來越多另人膽顫心驚的細節。而將整個故事故事推上都市傳說的就是在討論的最後，這個&quot;Mike&quot;說他去詢問了他母親關於蠟燭灣的事情。而他母親非常驚訝為什麼他會突然提起這個節目，因為當年的他每天都會在4點的時候吵着要看這一個節目。然後就打開電視，調到一個沒有節目的頻道，看着花白的螢幕30分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又會咁多人一齊對一件冇發生過嘅事有印象！？<br />\n香港有冇過類似嘅事呢？<br />\n好驚嚇到尿滲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今晚要開燈訓教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa16aa243ef4c4cb61418f9a53d1578e42441adb","tid":2315683,"uid":223912,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"天水圍六星陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a045f0feda830ff78125e0f8eb1dc8bd0520cf78","tid":2315683,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"唔記得睇咩美劇果時 聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b466000df9e8d23fae7bc43d21c1bd0c85b7c288","tid":2315683,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa16aa243ef4c4cb61418f9a53d1578e42441adb","tid":2315683,"uid":223912,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"天水圍六星陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"唔係天水圍六芒星咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再提了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958cf9b6bbf1c6ed9110743c63841e6d1095ac44","tid":2315683,"uid":66893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"有套美劇Channel Zero 第一季就係改編呢個故事"},{"pid":"c9c7e1af15e8a62a086ab14aa9357ddc3be9994b","tid":2315683,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa16aa243ef4c4cb61418f9a53d1578e42441adb","tid":2315683,"uid":223912,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"天水圍六星陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit